t;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="47" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_34.gif"/&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32001660&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=20671444326895608086bef5_69035691"/><published>2025-08-07T22:52:45+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>d772f7dbfa4d6783b05728202a34681e</id><title>港人需起碼500萬元儲蓄，才能夠安心退休</title><updated>2025-08-08T04:47:14+08:00</updated><author><name>逍遙老僧</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-08T04:47:14+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573519296"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573519296"&gt;80%表示傾向選擇「微退休」。大多數受訪者認為，最理想的「微退休」年齡是50歲後。他們也意識到這需要充分的財務準備，大部分表示需要累積超過200萬元資產，才會考慮「微退休」。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;「退休後再就業」亦廣受歡迎，大部分「退休後再就業」支持者願意接受較低薪酬，40%計劃在退休後6個月內重返職場。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;「微退休」及「退休後再就業」等新趨勢興起，凸顯投資策略也應與時俱進。不過，調查顯示多達40%受訪者沒有訂立退休儲蓄目標。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32001786&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=20671444326895608086bef5_69035691"/><published>2025-08-08T04:47:14+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>fc9acfb478e883004181161b78efc7c1</id><title>恒指夜期</title><updated>2025-08-08T04:58:12+08:00</updated><author><name>jeffreychou2002</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-08T04:58:12+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573519306"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573519306"&gt;恒指夜期回軟，截至今晨12時30分報24899點，跌133點，低水183點；ADR港股比例指數報24909點，較港收市低172點。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32001789&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=20671444326895608086bef5_69035691"/><published>2025-08-08T04:58:12+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>83d165f525b527770faed98cad1ea895</id><title>有一個好高深嘅問題請教</title><updated>2025-08-08T07:23:39+08:00</updated><author><name>吳儼晉</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-08T07:23:39+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573519689"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573519689"&gt;點解期貨近排先跌後拉？&lt;br&gt;昨晚終於真係跌&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16418584" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573519689" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250808/20250808_c576548151e8548b30bdQh58aYnLkhRb.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/14788f/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250808/20250808_c576548151e8548b30bdQh58aYnLkhRb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16418584_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16418584&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Screenshot_2025-08-08-07-22-01-365_cn.futu.trader-edit.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (483.95 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-8 07:23&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32001814&amp;extra=page%3D1%